remarks.format: ## Remarks 用于编译查询，并对查询进行缓存以供重复使用。Provides for compilation and caching of queries for reuse. 从概念上讲，此类包含具有若干重载的单个 `Compile` 方法。Conceptually this class contains a single `Compile` method with several overloads. 调用 `Compile` 方法可以创建新的委托来表示已编译的查询。You call the `Compile` method to create a new delegate to represent the compiled query. 在使用 输入参数值及其他参数值调用该委托时，它将生成某个结果（例如 实例）。The delegate, when invoked with the input parameter and other parameter values, produces some result (such as an instance). 首次调用该委托时，将转换并缓存查询。The query is translated and cached when the delegate is invoked for the first time. ## Examples 下面的示例将编译并调用一个查询，该查询接受 和 输入参数，并返回一个订单日期晚于 2003 年 3 月 8 日且应付款总额少于 300.00 美元的订单序列：The following example compiles and then invokes a query that accepts and input parameters and returns a sequence of orders where the order date is later than March 8, 2003 and the total due is less than $300.00: [!code-csharp[DP L2E Conceptual Examples#CompiledQuery5](~/samples/snippets/csharp/VS_Snippets_Data/DP L2E Conceptual Examples/CS/Program.cs#compiledquery5)] [!code-vb[DP L2E Conceptual Examples#CompiledQuery5](~/samples/snippets/visualbasic/VS_Snippets_Data/DP L2E Conceptual Examples/VB/Module1.vb#compiledquery5)]
